desc:
Target 1 face-up monster you control, then activate 1 of these effects;
● Equip 1 "Kanohi" Equip Spell from your hand or GY to that target.
● Banish 1 Level 1 Rock monster you control or in your GY with 0 ATK/DEF, and if you do, equip 1 "Great Kanohi" Equip Spell from your Deck to that target.

Activate 1 of these effects;
● Target any number of "Bahrag" cards you control; destroy them, then draw 1 card for each card destroyed.
● Shuffle 2 "Bahrag" cards you control with different names into the Extra Deck; send all cards on the field to the GY, except "Bohrok" and "Krana" cards.
